    • asteroids.model.World

  • public class World
extends java.lang.Object
    A class of worlds involving a size and entities.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Simon Merckx and Tobias Cornille, Simon Merckx and Tobias Cornille. We both study informatics (1ba). Private repo on https://github.com/tobiascornille/Asteroids Please send us an email with your account info so we can add you as a contributer.
    Invariants:
  • Each world can have its size as size .
        canHaveAsSize(this.getSize)
  • Each world must have proper entities.
        hasProperEntities()
